

To run a Von Karman test simply 

type: 

./run.single.orig.offload.gnu.x   --> single precision, original version, offload using gfortran

./run.single.fused.dc.nv.x --> single precision, fused version, do concurrent using nvfortran

bgk.input        --> input file used for the simulation
plot.gnu         --> gnuplot file to check the resulta (do modify accordingly)
probe_g.0000.dat --> reference dat
